description:
The Sabbath is a gift from God, available to everyone. In a world glorifying productivity and busyness, Sabbath rest is a beautiful gift for all. Explore more about what #Adventists believe in this series. #Sabbath

To watch the full episode, paste the link into your browser: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UCk2k-VkmXM
